# Backend Configuration

IMPORTANT: Copy this file to `.env` in the `backend/` directory and fill in the required values.

## Azure OpenAI Settings
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://<your-resource-name>.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=<your-api-key>
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT_NAME=gpt-4
AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-02-15-preview
AZURE_OPENAI_TEMPERATURE=0.0
AZURE_OPENAI_MAX_TOKENS=2000

## MongoDB Settings
MONGODB_CONNECTION_STRING=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@<cluster>.mongodb.net/?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_DATABASE_NAME=link2hire
MONGODB_COLLECTION_JOBS=jobs
MONGODB_COLLECTION_CONVERSATIONS=conversations

## Google Sheets Settings
# Path to Google Service Account JSON credentials file
GOOGLE_SHEETS_CREDENTIALS_PATH=./credentials/sheets-credentials.json
# Spreadsheet ID from the URL: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/{SPREADSHEET_ID}/edit
GOOGLE_SHEETS_SPREADSHEET_ID=<your-spreadsheet-id>
GOOGLE_SHEETS_WORKSHEET_NAME=Jobs

## LinkedIn Settings (Optional - Future Integration)
LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID=<your-client-id>
LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=<your-client-secret>
LINKEDIN_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8000/auth/linkedin/callback

## API Settings
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
DEBUG=False

## CORS Origins (comma-separated)
API_CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:4200,http://localhost:3000

## Timeouts
REQUEST_TIMEOUT=30
MAX_RETRIES=3
